Sentencas: LaBiMn2O6 (LBM) cathode for IT-SOFCs (intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells) has been prepared by solid state reaction and studied by XRD and EIS spectrum,respectively.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Properties of LaBiMn2O6 Cathode for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The results show that LBM has no reaction with Ce0.7Bi0.3O1.85(CBO) electrolyte at 1 000 degrees C for 12 h. AC impedance spectroscopy and DC polarization measurements are used to study the electrode performances.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Properties of LaBiMn2O6 Cathode for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The polarization resistance decreases with temperature and reaches 0.71 Omega.cm(2) at 700 degrees C in air.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Properties of LaBiMn2O6 Cathode for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: Oxygen partial pressure study indicated that charge transfer process is the major rate limiting step for LaBiMn2O6 cathode from 600 to 700 degrees C.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Properties of LaBiMn2O6 Cathode for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The LaBiMn2O6 cathode exhibits the lowest overpotential of 85 mV under current density of 216 mA .
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Properties of LaBiMn2O6 Cathode for IT-SOFCs
